description: Heldi website build system, always in force, brand rules, responsive contract, finishing gate
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

This repo has a locked design and copy system. Do not build from generic web
conventions.

- Rules and identity: read BRAND.md before copy or styling work (§11 is the
  change-impact map for product facts; §14 is the pre-flight checklist).
- Build procedure: read PLAYBOOK.md before adding or restructuring anything.
  §1 is the responsive contract: every surface ships two deliberate layouts,
  mobile (max-width 899px) and wide (min-width 900px), sized with fluid clamp(),
  structure changing only at that one breakpoint, verified at 375 and 1280
  minimum.
- Never: em dashes in copy, the word "scoop", literal #000, sans-serif type,
  soft blurred shadows, raw <img> tags, hard-coded prices (lib/pricing.ts is the
  source), health claims beyond protein's three verbatim register entries
  ("Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass" / "to the maintenance of
  muscle mass" / "to the maintenance of normal bones").
- Finishing gate for every change:
  npm run brand-lint && npm run typecheck && npm run build
  then view the change at a phone width and a wide width.
- Visual reference for every component: docs/brand/specimen.html.
